====================================
wordpress-cl    - post from your CLI
====================================

Simple posting program using wordpresslib

You can get wordpresslib from here:
http://www.blackbirdblog.it/programmazione/progetti/28#english

Just configure it (username and password and url of course!)
and use it this way:
wordpress-cl title postFile.wppost

the file.wppost should be a plain text file.
